WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:0
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:39.770 --> 00:01:43.350
They Believe in Me

3
00:01:43.350 --> 00:01:46.600
I understand your frustration.

4
00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:50.340
You tried to get up,
and I didn't let you.

5
00:01:50.340 --> 00:01:55.420
You tried to throw a left punch,
so I hit your left shoulder.

6
00:01:55.420 --> 00:01:59.950
You tried to throw a right punch,
so I hit your right shoulder.

7
00:01:59.950 --> 00:02:05.990
All of this shows that you're just an idiot
who can do nothing but feel frustrated.

8
00:02:05.990 --> 00:02:09.920
That's how it is when your
every move is easily predicted.

9
00:02:10.820 --> 00:02:15.380
But... I don't want to just
make you feel frustrated...

10
00:02:15.870 --> 00:02:19.620
Whether it's a left kick or a right kick...

11
00:02:19.620 --> 00:02:22.820
I'll hit you before you can do anything.

12
00:02:22.820 --> 00:02:28.200
And I'll keep it up
until your heart bursts in half.

13
00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:38.220
Every attack has an intent...

14
00:02:43.180 --> 00:02:44.810
and a presence!

15
00:02:49.460 --> 00:02:52.800
Don't just attack blindly, Luffy!

16
00:02:59.480 --> 00:03:00.520
Take this!

17
00:03:20.810 --> 00:03:22.790
As I thought...

18
00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:34.840
he's beginning to see the future
in the same way I do.

19
00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:48.530
Oh, shoot!

20
00:03:47.150 --> 00:03:53.160
Bege's Ship, At Sea

21
00:03:48.530 --> 00:03:49.430
What's wrong?

22
00:03:49.430 --> 00:03:52.950
I forgot to pipe roses of whipped cream

23
00:03:52.950 --> 00:03:55.580
on the top of the cake!

24
00:03:56.570 --> 00:03:58.740
I'll do it!

25
00:03:58.740 --> 00:04:00.380
Give me a pastry bag!

26
00:04:00.380 --> 00:04:01.160
Yes, sir!

27
00:04:01.590 --> 00:04:03.490
Sky Walk!

28
00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:18.680
Amazing!

29
00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:19.470
So beautiful!

30
00:04:21.910 --> 00:04:23.930
All right! It's finished!

31
00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:25.920
Yes!

32
00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:26.770
Finally!

33
00:04:26.770 --> 00:04:31.940
The ultimate wedding cake—one that will
stop Big Mom—is finished!

34
00:04:35.900 --> 00:04:39.450
It smells so good...
It's making me feel faint-rero.

35
00:04:39.450 --> 00:04:41.990
I don't know what else to say!

36
00:04:41.990 --> 00:04:45.640
We didn't even need to add any poison!

37
00:04:45.640 --> 00:04:49.810
I hope Big Mom will drop dead
from deliciousness!

38
00:04:55.850 --> 00:04:58.550
Great! We made it in time!

39
00:04:58.550 --> 00:04:59.970
Madam Pudding!

40
00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:02.150
What?!

41
00:05:04.470 --> 00:05:07.510
Hey, are you guys okay?!

42
00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:09.730
The cooks are collapsing one after another!

43
00:05:09.730 --> 00:05:12.970
They must have worked too hard!

44
00:05:27.730 --> 00:05:32.480
Don't stand up again.
We know your plan.

45
00:05:33.570 --> 00:05:36.400
"Cacao Island at one a.m.".

46
00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:41.340
But of course, your friends will be wiped out
before they even get close to Cacao Island.

47
00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:47.750
They will be greeted
by my younger brothers' fleets.

48
00:05:47.750 --> 00:05:52.630
It'll be the same for you,
even if you do manage to get out of here.

49
00:05:54.630 --> 00:05:55.880
But...

50
00:05:57.170 --> 00:06:02.340
I'll definitely...
make it through the mirror!

51
00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:10.480
Why are you talking like you'll succeed?

52
00:06:12.440 --> 00:06:14.860
Pudding-chan ! Chiffon-chan !

53
00:06:15.540 --> 00:06:18.460
I couldn't have done it without your help.
Thanks!

54
00:06:20.220 --> 00:06:21.670
With this cake...

55
00:06:22.300 --> 00:06:25.130
I can save my friends for sure!

56
00:06:29.260 --> 00:06:33.710
What makes you so certain?!
Sure, the cake is done,

57
00:06:33.710 --> 00:06:36.520
but your friends could be dead already!

58
00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:40.890
Even if they're alive, you don't know
whether Mama will like the cake or not!

59
00:06:40.890 --> 00:06:45.760
It's a waste of time to transport 
this crappy cake, Sanji...

60
00:06:45.760 --> 00:06:46.450
...-san !

61
00:06:47.820 --> 00:06:49.620
That's not what you meant to say, Pudding!

62
00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:54.660
Oh! No, I didn't mean it!
What am I saying?!

63
00:06:55.900 --> 00:06:59.150
In any case, I've got to get going...

64
00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:12.710
Wait!

65
00:07:14.580 --> 00:07:18.630
Wedding cake!

66
00:07:18.630 --> 00:07:21.530
Rumble! Monster Point!

67
00:07:26.010 --> 00:07:28.350
I will stop her!

68
00:07:28.350 --> 00:07:33.310
What the hell is that?!
Are there only monsters on that ship?!

69
00:07:33.310 --> 00:07:36.360
Napoleon! Extend yourself!

70
00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:38.240
Yes, Mama!

71
00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:46.200
Chopper, Brook, Jinbe!
If we can hold out here, then...

72
00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:48.530
Yeah, I know!

73
00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:50.740
You don't need to say it.

74
00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:53.360
Mm-hm!

75
00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:57.960
Until that moment comes,
endure it no matter what!

76
00:07:58.520 --> 00:08:03.160
I'll bring the best cake ever
to stop Big Mom...

77
00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:05.510
I'm gonna kick your ass...

78
00:08:07.720 --> 00:08:10.850
and make it through the mirror.

79
00:08:11.770 --> 00:08:13.140
Because they...

80
00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:17.480
...believe in me!

81
00:08:20.540 --> 00:08:22.940
I'll cut you in half!

82
00:08:22.940 --> 00:08:25.700
Cloven Palm!

83
00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:33.580
Chopper!

84
00:08:34.590 --> 00:08:36.120
Gust Sword!

85
00:08:44.820 --> 00:08:46.420
Soul Parade!

86
00:08:49.970 --> 00:08:51.760
Cognac!

87
00:08:51.760 --> 00:08:54.140
Stop!

88
00:09:06.530 --> 00:09:08.990
Chopper! You can't fight anymore!

89
00:09:08.990 --> 00:09:13.040
I've got no choice!
Come on, Big Mom!

90
00:09:13.040 --> 00:09:18.600
At the very least,
I can drag you down with me into the sea!

91
00:09:20.450 --> 00:09:22.430
You're full of spirit.

92
00:09:22.430 --> 00:09:26.210
Then, do you think you'll be able
to take me on after this?

93
00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:52.070
No... way...

94
00:09:56.950 --> 00:09:59.870
At that size, even seawater won't help us!

95
00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:03.000
So... that's the soul of an emperor!

96
00:10:07.430 --> 00:10:10.430
Now, try to get away as far as you can!

97
00:10:10.440 --> 00:10:14.640
If nothing is done,
we'll get burned up along with the Sunny !

98
00:10:15.790 --> 00:10:18.530
Even though we made it this far!

99
00:10:18.530 --> 00:10:21.400
And Sanji-kun should be here any moment now!

100
00:10:21.400 --> 00:10:25.240
You all showed me a good time...

101
00:10:25.240 --> 00:10:27.690
Now, give me the cake...

102
00:10:41.380 --> 00:10:42.960
What is this...

103
00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:46.170
delicious smell?

104
00:10:48.760 --> 00:10:51.830
Don't stand up again! You stand no chance!

105
00:10:56.170 --> 00:11:01.430
This fool's observation haki is
getting as good as mine!

106
00:11:20.530 --> 00:11:24.740
I have to get rid of him soon,
or something unexpected could happen!

107
00:11:28.390 --> 00:11:29.530
Mochi...

108
00:11:31.850 --> 00:11:33.250
Thrust!

109
00:11:50.580 --> 00:11:52.090
That ship...

110
00:11:55.220 --> 00:11:56.290
Guys!

111
00:11:58.300 --> 00:12:00.040
A ship is here!

112
00:12:01.460 --> 00:12:03.630
It's got the cake onboard!

113
00:12:08.180 --> 00:12:11.510
Sanji-kun and the others
baked the cake and came back for us!

114
00:12:11.510 --> 00:12:13.480
Oh, Sanji!

115
00:12:13.480 --> 00:12:15.480
Sanji-san !

116
00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:16.890
Mama!

117
00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:22.480
It smells so sweet!

118
00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:29.870
There it is, Black Leg. It's your ship!

119
00:12:29.870 --> 00:12:35.250
That damn Prometheus.
He's gotten huge because of Big Mom's soul!

120
00:12:35.250 --> 00:12:39.580
And riding on top of the giant Prometheus,
I see Big Mom-rero.

121
00:12:39.580 --> 00:12:42.590
Father! Beyond them, it's...

122
00:12:42.590 --> 00:12:44.210
Perospero and...

123
00:12:44.210 --> 00:12:45.590
Bavarois...

124
00:12:45.590 --> 00:12:48.050
along with Smoothie and the others!

125
00:12:48.050 --> 00:12:52.310
They're being chased by
quite a troublesome fleet!

126
00:12:52.310 --> 00:12:54.900
Their ship's taken heavy damage, too!

127
00:12:58.100 --> 00:13:00.250
Man your positions, men!

128
00:13:00.250 --> 00:13:01.690
Yeah!

129
00:13:01.690 --> 00:13:05.710
We're up against Big Mom!
Keep your guards up!

130
00:13:05.710 --> 00:13:10.450
But if you see an opening,
fill her with bullets!

131
00:13:10.450 --> 00:13:14.260
– Yeah!
– Rero !

132
00:13:21.690 --> 00:13:26.090
Nami-san ! I'm here to save you!

133
00:13:26.090 --> 00:13:32.650
Anyway, Big Mom and Perospero
have to have been chasing them for hours...

134
00:13:32.650 --> 00:13:37.100
I'm impressed that they survived!
Especially without a captain to lead them!

135
00:13:37.100 --> 00:13:39.890
Nami-swan !

136
00:13:39.890 --> 00:13:43.440
There's someone on the bow!
Do you feel that weird aura?!

137
00:13:43.440 --> 00:13:48.740
Well, it isn't haki...
Why are they on Bege's ship?

138
00:13:48.740 --> 00:13:52.010
Hm? Someone's dancing
on the bow of that ship!

139
00:13:52.010 --> 00:13:55.990
Who cares about that?!
The cake is what matters!

140
00:13:56.040 --> 00:13:57.760
Lick!

141
00:13:57.760 --> 00:14:04.050
They definitely recreated the cake
that we saw at the wedding!

142
00:14:05.630 --> 00:14:11.340
If Mama likes how it tastes,
her ravenous rampage will end! But...

143
00:14:11.340 --> 00:14:16.220
Bege is there!
That cake has to be poisoned!

144
00:14:16.220 --> 00:14:20.720
What should I do?!

145
00:14:24.190 --> 00:14:29.110
Thanks to that sweet smell,
she's stopped attacking us...

146
00:14:29.110 --> 00:14:30.380
I thought...

147
00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:33.490
we were going to die...

148
00:14:34.710 --> 00:14:37.370
Should we destroy that cake?!

149
00:14:37.370 --> 00:14:42.150
No, if we do that, there will be
no stopping Mama's ravenous rampage,

150
00:14:42.150 --> 00:14:44.010
and this country will be annihilated!

151
00:14:44.010 --> 00:14:47.560
Oh... but, if she eats
the poisoned cake and dies...

152
00:14:47.560 --> 00:14:50.810
it'll be the end for both this country
and our pirate crew!

153
00:14:50.810 --> 00:14:54.930
What should I do?!
Which option should I choose?!

154
00:14:56.450 --> 00:14:58.050
Hey, Black Leg!

155
00:14:59.490 --> 00:15:04.590
We held up our end of the deal!
Now we'll take the cake.

156
00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:11.940
As promised, we won't do a thing
until Mama eats it and is full.

157
00:15:11.940 --> 00:15:13.570
But...

158
00:15:14.140 --> 00:15:16.910
after that, we're free to do
 whatever we want, got it?!

159
00:15:16.910 --> 00:15:23.400
Do whatever you want. Our mission was
to pacify Big Mom with this cake.

160
00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:25.820
We can stop her!

161
00:15:25.820 --> 00:15:28.300
We're ready, Sanji...

162
00:15:29.180 --> 00:15:30.280
...-san !

163
00:15:30.280 --> 00:15:31.430
I'm coming!

164
00:15:31.430 --> 00:15:34.420
You'd better hurry up
if you don't want to die!

165
00:15:34.950 --> 00:15:36.200
Pudding!

166
00:15:37.950 --> 00:15:40.600
Take care of yourself!

167
00:15:43.010 --> 00:15:45.090
Are you happy now?

168
00:15:45.990 --> 00:15:47.130
Yes, very...

169
00:15:47.900 --> 00:15:50.600
Goodbye, Sister...

170
00:15:53.580 --> 00:15:56.440
Rabiyan! Super Express!

171
00:15:59.180 --> 00:16:02.570
Go fast enough so that Big Brother Peros
and Big Brother Bavarois don't notice us!

172
00:16:02.570 --> 00:16:03.490
Okay!

173
00:16:09.220 --> 00:16:13.580
My wedding cake!

174
00:16:13.580 --> 00:16:15.370
There it is!

175
00:16:17.980 --> 00:16:20.960
I finally found it! Let's go!

176
00:16:20.980 --> 00:16:22.090
Yes!

177
00:16:22.090 --> 00:16:23.260
Mama!

178
00:16:23.280 --> 00:16:28.350
Wedding cake!

179
00:16:28.350 --> 00:16:31.160
Here she comes! To starboard!

180
00:16:31.160 --> 00:16:31.890
Yes, sir!

181
00:16:31.890 --> 00:16:37.350
Full speed southwest!
Head toward Liqueur Island!

182
00:16:40.150 --> 00:16:41.610
Lick?

183
00:16:41.610 --> 00:16:46.240
Minister Perospero!
The ship with the cake has changed course!

184
00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:47.200
Why?!

185
00:16:47.200 --> 00:16:51.490
Mama is being lured by the cake
and has started chasing Bege's ship!

186
00:16:51.490 --> 00:16:54.600
Straw Hat's ship and Bege's ship...

187
00:16:54.600 --> 00:16:59.260
By splitting up,
they're trying to divide us...

188
00:16:59.260 --> 00:17:00.790
Lick!

189
00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:05.670
Yo! I'm back!

190
00:17:05.670 --> 00:17:06.650
Sanji-kun !

191
00:17:06.650 --> 00:17:08.590
Sanji-san ! Pudding-san !

192
00:17:08.590 --> 00:17:10.370
Sanji!

193
00:17:10.370 --> 00:17:13.800
We were barely hanging on!
I thought we were done for! Thank you!

194
00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:16.250
I'm glad that you're okay!

195
00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:22.440
Thump!

196
00:17:22.820 --> 00:17:25.650
I love you, too! Nami-swan !

197
00:17:26.720 --> 00:17:30.500
By the way, Sanji-san,
why were you on Bege's ship?

198
00:17:32.540 --> 00:17:34.440
It's a long story...

199
00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:37.410
Where is Bege's ship heading?

200
00:17:38.090 --> 00:17:42.580
We don't know what Mom will do
after she eats the cake...

201
00:17:42.580 --> 00:17:46.880
so they're taking the cake
to the nearest island.

202
00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:50.400
What? So they decided to be bait?!

203
00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:53.030
Why are they doing that?!

204
00:17:53.030 --> 00:17:55.910
They haven't given up on killing her.

205
00:17:55.910 --> 00:17:58.180
I see. That sounds just like Bege.

206
00:17:58.910 --> 00:18:02.110
This ship's safety is the only thing
that matters to me.

207
00:18:02.110 --> 00:18:05.960
It'll be great if they can lure Mom away.

208
00:18:05.960 --> 00:18:07.190
In any case...

209
00:18:08.700 --> 00:18:10.710
Our ship has taken a lot of damage...

210
00:18:10.710 --> 00:18:13.320
I'm sorry. I should've done better...

211
00:18:13.320 --> 00:18:18.040
What are you talking about, Jinbe?!
If it weren't for you, we probably would have...

212
00:18:18.040 --> 00:18:21.650
Let's talk about it later.
I'm really glad that you're okay.

213
00:18:22.930 --> 00:18:26.710
By the way,
where are Pedro and Carrot-chan ?

214
00:18:30.940 --> 00:18:32.200
Um...

215
00:18:32.200 --> 00:18:37.440
Oh, th-they're sleeping inside!
They both got exhausted from fighting...

216
00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:41.730
Brother Peros, what should we do?!

217
00:18:41.730 --> 00:18:44.190
Straw Hat's ship or Mama,
which one should we chase?!

218
00:18:50.690 --> 00:18:53.110
This is... Bege...

219
00:18:53.110 --> 00:18:56.830
Bege! You bastard!
What are you up to?!

220
00:18:56.830 --> 00:18:59.880
And why is the cake on your ship?!

221
00:19:01.190 --> 00:19:05.180
We'll deal with Mama's ravenous rampage.

222
00:19:05.180 --> 00:19:08.160
We'll let her eat the cake
and then make sure she's comfortable.

223
00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:13.590
Don't lie, you traitor!
What did you put in the cake?!

224
00:19:13.590 --> 00:19:19.250
We didn't put anything in it.
You know Pudding made the cake, right?

225
00:19:19.250 --> 00:19:22.300
Oh, yeah! Where's Pudding?!

226
00:19:22.300 --> 00:19:28.080
You don't need to worry
about Mama or Pudding right now.

227
00:19:28.080 --> 00:19:30.660
Just relax and focus on the Straw Hats.

228
00:19:30.660 --> 00:19:31.980
You son of a–

229
00:19:34.230 --> 00:19:36.150
Hey, Bege!

230
00:19:36.560 --> 00:19:38.950
Let's chase Bege, Bavarois!

231
00:19:38.950 --> 00:19:39.860
What?!

232
00:19:39.860 --> 00:19:44.990
Look at them! I'm one hundred percent sure
that they're scheming to kill Mama.

233
00:19:44.990 --> 00:19:47.950
And Pudding might be dead!

234
00:19:47.950 --> 00:19:51.750
But Brother Peros!
What about the Straw Hats' ship?!

235
00:19:52.010 --> 00:19:55.900
They'll sink at Cacao Island anyway! Also...

236
00:19:57.210 --> 00:20:01.340
Who do you think is also
chasing the Straw Hats' ship?

237
00:20:02.630 --> 00:20:03.300
Oh, yeah!

238
00:20:03.300 --> 00:20:05.170
Answer!

239
00:20:05.910 --> 00:20:09.910
Are you still chasing the Straw Hats' ship,
Smoothie?!

240
00:20:10.140 --> 00:20:16.400
Charlotte Smoothie
14th Daughter of the Charlotte Family
(One of the Three Sweet Commanders)

241
00:20:11.590 --> 00:20:14.000
Yeah, I am, Brother.

242
00:20:16.400 --> 00:20:20.460
You guys keep chasing the Straw Hats' ship!

243
00:20:23.150 --> 00:20:26.370
Bavarois and I are going
to chase Bege and Mama!

244
00:20:29.180 --> 00:20:34.670
Squeeze every last drop of life out of them!

245
00:20:34.670 --> 00:20:39.920
Torment them and plunge them
into an abyss of fear!

246
00:20:39.920 --> 00:20:41.580
Roger that.

247
00:20:42.800 --> 00:20:46.140
He should've just let me handle it
from the beginning...

248
00:20:46.990 --> 00:20:50.180
Brother Peros is getting distracted...

249
00:20:53.140 --> 00:20:59.400
Charlotte Citron
15th Daughter of the Charlotte Family

250
00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:56.980
Staying on Cacao Island would've been much easier,

251
00:20:56.980 --> 00:20:59.400
eating chocolate and drinking tea...

252
00:21:00.380 --> 00:21:03.800
They're so impatient.
Men are such idiots.

253
00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:09.750
Charlotte Cinnamon
16th Daughter of the Charlotte Family

254
00:21:12.660 --> 00:21:14.210
Well, don't say that.

255
00:21:20.390 --> 00:21:23.180
Everyone, prepare to fight!

256
00:21:23.180 --> 00:21:28.040
Before they reach Cacao Island,
we'll sink the Straw Hats' ship!

257
00:21:28.040 --> 00:21:29.900
Yeah!

258
00:21:30.370 --> 00:21:31.590
Mm-hm!

259
00:21:31.590 --> 00:21:32.410
Mm-hm!

260
00:21:36.690 --> 00:21:39.690
They know where we're meeting Luffy?!

261
00:21:40.640 --> 00:21:45.000
Yeah, it's probably surrounded 
by ships waiting to ambush us.

262
00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:46.810
Oh, no...

263
00:21:46.810 --> 00:21:51.650
Oddly enough, they seem to be
acknowledging us as strong opponents.

264
00:21:51.650 --> 00:21:56.700
Cacao Island will be
our final and biggest challenge!

265
00:21:56.700 --> 00:22:00.470
We'll rescue Luffy no matter what
and escape this territory.

266
00:22:00.470 --> 00:22:05.790
But... if we fight their fleet head-on, we're bound to lose.

267
00:22:17.040 --> 00:22:19.380
What's with that pitiful look?!

268
00:22:38.570 --> 00:22:41.220
I can't believe you slipped...

269
00:22:48.850 --> 00:22:51.230
Straw Hat!

270
00:22:54.180 --> 00:22:56.210
My plan is going well!

271
00:23:10.790 --> 00:23:14.920
Big Brother!

272
00:23:23.030 --> 00:23:23.840
Cling!

273
00:23:23.840 --> 00:23:26.250
To tell you the truth,
I was the one who...

274
00:23:26.250 --> 00:23:28.700
Oh, I didn't know that, Flambé!

275
00:23:28.700 --> 00:23:31.140
You're such a thoughtful,
well-behaved girl!

276
00:23:34.430 --> 00:23:37.750
That's my favorite sister.

277
00:23:39.920 --> 00:23:43.820
Oh, I'm so commendable! And so cute!

278
00:23:51.350 --> 00:23:53.510
That one moment of carelessness...

279
00:23:55.680 --> 00:23:57.930
will be the deciding factor in this fight!

280
00:24:06.180 --> 00:24:08.160
Why did you lower your guard?!

281
00:24:28.030 --> 00:24:29.350
Mochi Anemone!

282
00:24:38.150 --> 00:24:40.360
What's the matter, Straw Hat?!

283
00:25:06.240 --> 00:25:09.250
Just as I began to think highly of you...

284
00:25:12.840 --> 00:25:15.270
you decided to disappoint me!

285
00:25:41.820 --> 00:25:43.690
I think I saw it!

286
00:25:44.900 --> 00:25:46.190
Or was it my imagination?

287
00:25:48.070 --> 00:25:49.970
That's fine.

288
00:25:50.780 --> 00:25:55.000
Because beyond that imagination
is observation haki!

289
00:26:01.030 --> 00:26:05.010
You have to be able
to sense it instinctively!

290
00:26:05.010 --> 00:26:06.730
Instinctively?!

291
00:26:15.920 --> 00:26:17.620
He stood up again!

292
00:26:17.620 --> 00:26:19.540
What's with those wobbly legs?!

293
00:26:20.290 --> 00:26:22.590
All right! Another shot, then!

294
00:26:25.090 --> 00:26:31.260
This time, I'll shoot a numbing needle
that's 10 times more effective than the last one!

295
00:26:34.340 --> 00:26:37.280
You're just a monkey who
doesn't know when to give up.

296
00:26:37.280 --> 00:26:39.500
Drop dead already!

297
00:26:46.070 --> 00:26:47.090
Numbing Needle!

298
00:27:02.350 --> 00:27:06.300
What? He dodged it!
That was my silent needle!

299
00:27:12.170 --> 00:27:14.180
But he fell anyway!

300
00:27:51.090 --> 00:27:53.920
Lady Flambé! They'll hear us!

301
00:27:53.920 --> 00:27:57.930
B-But the way that monkey stands up...

302
00:27:57.930 --> 00:28:01.100
It reminds me of a newborn fawn!

303
00:28:01.100 --> 00:28:02.530
So wobbly!

304
00:28:04.430 --> 00:28:07.260
Come on, don't make us laugh, too!

305
00:28:07.260 --> 00:28:08.730
There, look!

306
00:28:08.730 --> 00:28:12.950
He's so lame! Even though he's
super weak and covered in blood,

307
00:28:12.950 --> 00:28:15.550
he gets up again and again!

308
00:28:18.860 --> 00:28:21.890
He wobbles up
then gets knocked back down!

309
00:28:21.890 --> 00:28:24.020
And then wobbles his way back up again!

310
00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:28.650
Flambé...?

311
00:28:40.590 --> 00:28:41.740
Don't tell me...

312
00:28:55.230 --> 00:28:57.470
Big Brother is looking this way!

313
00:28:57.470 --> 00:29:00.600
He's so perfect and so cool!

314
00:29:05.350 --> 00:29:08.940
Oh, Commander Katakuri
is coming this way!

315
00:29:08.940 --> 00:29:10.880
What?!

316
00:29:13.170 --> 00:29:17.990
Well done!
You're such a well-behaved girl, Flambé...

317
00:29:17.990 --> 00:29:19.390
There, there.

318
00:29:19.390 --> 00:29:21.450
He's going to praise me!

319
00:29:23.040 --> 00:29:26.540
I'm not ready for it yet!

320
00:29:27.790 --> 00:29:32.170
I see. It was you, Flambé.

321
00:29:35.770 --> 00:29:40.510
You stopped him with your
favorite silent blowgun.

322
00:29:43.830 --> 00:29:49.300
In such an intense battle,
his concentration suddenly broke...

323
00:29:50.350 --> 00:29:52.900
I thought it was strange...

324
00:29:54.620 --> 00:29:56.150
Mochi...

325
00:29:58.320 --> 00:29:59.200
Thrust!

326
00:30:01.910 --> 00:30:07.500
But I still attacked him in his moment of weakness, pierced his stomach, and inflicted a fatal wound!

327
00:30:11.050 --> 00:30:15.880
Do you think...
that I want to win like that?!

328
00:30:15.880 --> 00:30:20.590
Look at that, Lady Flambé!
The fawn stood up again!

329
00:30:21.470 --> 00:30:23.550
Hey, don't make me laugh!

330
00:30:23.550 --> 00:30:25.000
His legs are all wobbly!

331
00:30:25.000 --> 00:30:26.820
Just like a baby fawn's!

332
00:30:29.800 --> 00:30:33.400
Now, Commander Katakuri will win for sure!

333
00:30:34.730 --> 00:30:36.370
Of course!

334
00:30:36.370 --> 00:30:40.780
It's my perfect big brother's
perfect victory!

335
00:30:41.450 --> 00:30:42.620
Flambé.

336
00:30:45.020 --> 00:30:46.660
Did you do it?

337
00:30:46.660 --> 00:30:48.950
That's right, Big Brother!

338
00:30:49.490 --> 00:30:52.470
I. Did. It.

339
00:30:52.470 --> 00:30:57.630
I'm the most considerate and the cutest
among your sisters, right?!

340
00:30:57.630 --> 00:31:01.760
The perfect and world's greatest big brother's favorite will be...

341
00:31:01.760 --> 00:31:04.140
me!

342
00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:07.640
Pat my head and tell me I'm a good girl!

343
00:31:07.640 --> 00:31:10.730
Big Brother!

344
00:31:11.980 --> 00:31:15.400
What do you all find so funny?!

345
00:31:37.470 --> 00:31:38.680
He...!

346
00:31:44.560 --> 00:31:46.850
Commander Katakuri!

347
00:31:47.450 --> 00:31:49.580
W-Why?!

348
00:31:57.470 --> 00:31:59.750
Don't you dare...

349
00:32:03.140 --> 00:32:06.790
give unwanted support
in a duel between men!

350
00:32:09.960 --> 00:32:11.460
Stay away for me!
Don't touch me!

351
00:32:12.670 --> 00:32:13.840
Ouch!

352
00:32:14.600 --> 00:32:16.220
Commander Katakuri!

353
00:32:22.850 --> 00:32:25.590
If you're going to laugh at that idiot...

354
00:32:25.590 --> 00:32:28.310
then you'll have to laugh at me, too!

355
00:32:46.380 --> 00:32:48.790
So lame!

356
00:32:52.660 --> 00:32:55.250
Agreed! So disappointing!

357
00:32:55.250 --> 00:32:59.000
Come on, that's gross!
You got blood on me!

358
00:32:59.000 --> 00:33:00.380
What the hell is this?!

359
00:33:00.380 --> 00:33:05.180
You're supposed to always be noble, calm, strong,
and perfect in every way!

360
00:33:05.180 --> 00:33:08.370
That's the person we admire!

361
00:33:08.400 --> 00:33:10.970
But you stabbed your own stomach...

362
00:33:10.970 --> 00:33:15.810
So lame! Someone like you
can not be Big Brother Katakuri!

363
00:33:15.810 --> 00:33:17.510
How pathetic!

364
00:33:18.980 --> 00:33:21.190
You look like a pelican eel!

365
00:33:22.920 --> 00:33:24.990
Pelican eel!

366
00:33:24.990 --> 00:33:29.110
Stop it, Lady Flambé!
We won't be able to hold in our laughter!

367
00:33:29.110 --> 00:33:32.530
C'mon... How disappointing!

368
00:33:34.900 --> 00:33:37.200
Whoa, it's a pelican eel!

369
00:33:37.200 --> 00:33:38.570
Stay away from him!

370
00:33:38.570 --> 00:33:41.940
And he's as strong as a monster!

371
00:33:41.940 --> 00:33:43.390
Run!

372
00:33:49.800 --> 00:33:52.720
Hey! Say something!

373
00:34:12.580 --> 00:34:15.950
Hurry up and take pictures!
Let's show everyone

374
00:34:15.950 --> 00:34:18.380
that loser's face!

375
00:34:26.360 --> 00:34:30.010
E-Excuse me!
I'm sorry, Commander Katakuri...

376
00:34:32.890 --> 00:34:35.850
Commander Katakuri, look this way!

377
00:34:35.850 --> 00:34:38.820
He really looks like a pelican eel.

378
00:34:39.850 --> 00:34:45.270
The perfect big brother
that everyone admired, Charlotte Katakuri,

379
00:34:45.270 --> 00:34:46.530
is dead!

380
00:34:46.530 --> 00:34:50.360
I'll expose you to the fan club
and to every island in Totto Land!

381
00:34:51.120 --> 00:34:53.480
It will be known
throughout the entire country!

382
00:34:53.480 --> 00:34:55.830
How dare you get
your dirty blood on me...

383
00:34:55.830 --> 00:34:59.370
and threaten me...
everyone's favorite?!

384
00:34:59.370 --> 00:35:03.220
Now who's the perfect big brother?!
You're so uncool!

385
00:35:03.220 --> 00:35:06.350
I'm embarrassed to even
tell people we're blood-related!

386
00:35:08.110 --> 00:35:12.410
You ruined the tea party and I won't 
forgive you, either, Straw Hat!

387
00:35:14.060 --> 00:35:17.080
It's so annoying
to even lay eyes on you two!

388
00:35:17.080 --> 00:35:21.630
I'll shoot highly venomous needles
through your hearts now!

389
00:35:21.630 --> 00:35:23.520
Do it! Do it!

390
00:35:23.520 --> 00:35:27.010
I won't forgive you!
Both of you should prepare for what's to come!

391
00:35:32.570 --> 00:35:35.100
Our spectators sure are noisy...

392
00:35:37.050 --> 00:35:39.520
They won't be able
to stay on their feet anyway!

393
00:36:01.720 --> 00:36:02.790
Conqueror's haki?!

394
00:36:03.490 --> 00:36:05.800
That monkey can use it, too?!

395
00:36:05.800 --> 00:36:08.090
A weakling like him...?!
